On Mon, Dec 18, 2023 at 9:05 PM Heath Maguire - Wolf IQ heath@wolfiq.com.au wrote:
Hi Jack,

Thanks for the Christmas wishes. I hope yourself and Maria sneak in a nice break too. I'll be off from Christmas to the last week of Jan... Heading north with the fam :slightly_smiling_face:.

We will whip these changes up for you tomorrow.

Regarding the April move, that's amazing news. Would you believe we started the current site in April, 5 years ago!

I'm glad you messaged as I will need to secure you a space for the rebuild. Broadly speaking the timeline will be:

March 2024, we commence to design a new site for your approval and loop in your SEO and SEM agencies to capture their wish lists
Mid March we code the site using the latest tech in WordPress
April, once the fit out is complete, we arrange a photoshoot and video walkthrough (we can recommend some of our partners, or work with yours)
Approx 2 weeks after we receive the stills and video, we go live with the new site. This will also give the Artiste team time to 'settle in', before the marketing ramps up

We have already booked out Jan and Feb, so ideally I want to secure a space for you in March. If this sounds good, I can quote you on a similar sized website for you to review/approve. We can then block out March for Artiste and brief in the details early next year. Let me know what you think?

Also, if you have any visuals of new space please send them my way. I'd love to see how it's going to come together and to ponder the new look over the break.


Thanks and speak soon,

Heath Maguire
Creative Director
